WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:10.501 --> 00:00:13.667
As the wait for the 2nd ECO Car (BOI) for Thai market has ended,

00:00:15.334 --> 00:00:17.634
The wait for the 3rd begins

00:00:20.134 --> 00:00:22.434
A whole new World Class small car from Mitsubishi

00:00:22.501 --> 00:00:25.267
Which will surely stunned the world

00:00:32.367 --> 00:00:34.901
After premiered in latest Geneva Motor Show,

00:00:35.267 --> 00:00:37.534
now it's chance for Thais to see it here

00:00:45.201 --> 00:00:47.467
Project commenced at Okazaki , Japan

00:00:47.901 --> 00:00:50.734
This concept vehicle lives by a factor called: The 7 E's

00:00:51.000 --> 00:00:55.601
These 7 E's are: Engineering, Efficient, Effective, Economy, EV, Environment, Export

00:00:56.601 --> 00:01:00.401
A 5-seater with short front end

00:01:03.734 --> 00:01:07.667
Just a small car but with better ideas

00:01:08.701 --> 00:01:13.501
With truly effective design all-round, as one of 7 E's

00:01:19.434 --> 00:01:24.234
With its possibility of fuel economy at rate 20 km/l

00:01:29.834 --> 00:01:33.134
Expecting that the standard production version would come with MIVEC engine, with MT or CVT transmission

00:01:37.867 --> 00:01:41.267
Featuring Idle-stop system with energy recharging while deceleration

00:01:43.201 --> 00:01:47.067
But it's also designed to be compatible with electric motor and battery right from the start

00:01:47.167 --> 00:01:49.701
So it's surely have its potential to convert to be a pure EV

00:01:53.267 --> 00:01:56.867
Another thing is for sure, Mitsubishi's production plant in Thailand has been selected to produce the production version of it

00:02:07.701 --> 00:02:13.301
Not a year away, a new good and fun value will be occured at Earth

00:02:17.267 --> 00:02:20.301
And yet... The I-MiEV is still here

